                            <comment id="13405396" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 2 Jul 2012 22:25:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, looks like there are two places to fix: one in getExpectedCompactedFileSize that I&apos;ve attached a fix for, and another in STCS from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4022&quot; title=&quot;Compaction of hints can get stuck in a loop&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-4022&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-4022&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Not sure off the top of my head how to fix that one so I&apos;ll leave to Yuki. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13405397" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 2 Jul 2012 22:27:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Decided to split the second part out to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4404&quot; title=&quot;tombstone estimation needs to avoid using global partitioner against index sstables&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-4404&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-4404&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; since it affects only 1.2.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
